@node "Install" "FileCheck - Installation"

The     Files     in    the    directories    'FileChecker/mbeigene'    and
'FileChecker/mbbatch'  have to be installed to the AMMS:  logic-path.  Copy
the rest to the corresponding system-directories.

But,  that's  not  all!   FileCheck  has to be configured.  See the Chapter
@{"Configuration " link "config" 0} on how to configure FileCheck.
@endnode


