--[settingsfile for FileCheck V3.00+]--------------------------------------

LEAVE LINE BLANK (ONLY LF) TO SKIP PART

@{" LINE 01: " link "filecheck.config" 4} LHA/LZX/LZH    ADDY       ( PATTERN ALLOWED )
@{" LINE 02: " link "filecheck.config" 8} ZIP         COMMENT
@{" LINE 03: " link "filecheck.config" 12} ZIP            ADDY       ( PATTERN ALLOWED )
@{" LINE 04: " link "filecheck.config" 16} TXT-FRONT      ADDY
@{" LINE 05: " link "filecheck.config" 19} TXT-END        ADDY
@{" LINE 06: " link "filecheck.config" 22} MAPUS   ADD-OPTIONS
@{" LINE 07: " link "filecheck.config" 37} MAPUS STRIP-OPTIONS
@{" LINE 08: " link "filecheck.config" 44} HOLD DIRECTORY            ( SYSOP'S PRIVATE DIR )
@{" LINE 09: " link "filecheck.config" 51} FILE_ID-STRIPCHARS        ( ASCII/EXAMPLE: 13 26 )
@{" LINE 10: " link "filecheck.config" 55} FILE_ID-CONVERTCHARS      ( IBM-MODE / EXAMPLE: 50=51 )
@{" LINE 11: " link "filecheck.config" 59} FILE_ID-CONVERTCHARS      ( AMIGA-MODE )
@{" LINE 12: " link "filecheck.config" 62} LINEADD         ADDY      ( ENV-VARS ALLOWED E.G. ${FILE} )
@{" LINE 13: " link "filecheck.config" 66} SETRETURN: FILE_ID
@{" LINE 14: " link "filecheck.config" 69} SETRETURN: NO FILE_ID
