@{" LINE 16: " link "filecheck.config" 76} SETRETURN: DUPLICATE/MOVE
@{" LINE 17: " link "filecheck.config" 80} SETRETURN: CORRUPT
@{" LINE 18: " link "filecheck.config" 83} SETRETURN: CORRUPT/MOVE
@{" LINE 19: " link "filecheck.config" 87} TEMPDIR

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode


@node "ENV-Vars" "FileCheck - ENV-Vars"

The  following  ENV-Vars  will  be set by AMMS.  They are also active after
FileCheck has ended.

@{b}These ENV-Vars will only be set if they are not known before@{ub}

 ${FILE}       : Path und filename
 ${PATHPART}   : Path
 ${FILEPART}   : Filename
 ${BOARD}      : fileboard-name
 ${PORT}       : Portname
 ${NAME}       : Username
 ${FC_LANGUAGE}: Languagestring (choosen language)


@{b}These  ENV-Vars  will  be set by FileCheck.  It does'nt matter whether they
exist before or not.@{ub}

 ${FC_FILETYPE}: Filetype
 ${FC_FSIZE1}  : Filelength (12345)
 ${FC_FSIZE2}  : Filelength (0012345)
 ${FC_FSIZE3}  : Filelength (  12345)
 ${FC_DAY}     : Date (Day)
 ${FC_MONTH}   : Date (Month)
 ${FC_YEAR}    : Date (Year)
 ${FC_HOUR}    : Time (Hours)
 ${FC_MIN}     : Time (Minutes)
 ${FC_SEC}     : Time (Seconds)
 ${FC_RDDAY}   : Date of distribution (Day)
 ${FC_RDMONTH} : Date of distribution (Month)
 ${FC_RDYEAR}  : Date of distribution (Year)
 ${FC_VERSION} : Version
 ${FC_REVISION}: Revision
 ${FC_REGISTER}: Registration-String
@endnode
